item.title: Honours Project
item.description: I undertook my honours during my fourth year of university. In my research project, I wanted to experiment with different types of dataset collection and preprocessing methodologies and how they affected the performance of Topic models (a type of AI model). The goal of a topic model is to summarise a long piece of text/s by examining the co-occurrence patterns of words and organising the words it sees into a ’topic'.

item.title: Data Analytics Project: Annalysing Australian Trade 2023
item.description: The visulisations in this post are demonstrations of skills in excel and tableau (although tableau visulisations do not have interactivity as intended due to licensing issues). Introduction This page is a report on data about Australian international trade. This report will highlight key information and trends on Australian international imports and exports with data that spans from 1988 - 2022. This report will also focus on the import & export main category of ‘0: food and live animals’ for closer analysis.
